How can this be?

00:26:48.460 --> 00:26:50.020
How can this happen?

00:26:50.940 --> 00:26:53.580
How am I supposed to face the City Lord now?

00:26:54.020 --> 00:26:54.980
It's all my fault.

00:26:55.380 --> 00:26:56.220
Yuzhai.

00:26:56.340 --> 00:26:57.460
I got ahead of myself

00:26:57.900 --> 00:26:59.860
and that's why he's dead.

00:27:01.180 --> 00:27:03.140
Oh, my little martial brother.

00:27:05.420 --> 00:27:06.020
Wushuang...

00:27:09.220 --> 00:27:10.060
Why are you here?

00:27:11.540 --> 00:27:12.700
He was fast

00:27:13.100 --> 00:27:14.620
and I got tired of chasing, so I fell asleep.

00:27:17.620 --> 00:27:18.300
I'm going to hit you!

