He is powerful.

00:27:32.380 --> 00:27:33.340
He could have killed you easily.

00:27:33.980 --> 00:27:34.380
I'm glad you're fine.

00:27:34.900 --> 00:27:35.940
What should we do now then?

00:27:37.580 --> 00:27:38.940
Even if we return to Belle's Manor now,

00:27:39.420 --> 00:27:40.580
we won't get what we're after.

00:27:42.380 --> 00:27:42.980
