00:38:45.020 --> 00:38:45.660
(Bone Nail.)

00:38:46.140 --> 00:38:46.740
(Iron Spike.)

00:38:47.140 --> 00:38:47.900
(Dragon Needle.)

00:38:49.060 --> 00:38:50.420
(You only have one chance.)

00:38:50.980 --> 00:38:52.060
